          "date": "2011-10-05 15:29:38.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-723 Remove Linux 2.6 requirement to enable ldiskfs",
        "message": "LU-723 Remove Linux 2.6 requirement to enable ldiskfs\n\nThe LB_LINUX_VERSION test now runs after LB_PATH_LDISKFS, but the\nldiskfs tests depended on the detected kernel version.  Thus\nconfigure was disabling ldiskfs by default.  At this point we can\nsafely assume that Lustre is being built on Linux version 2.6 or\nnewer, so we can simply remove the kernel version dependency when\ndetermining whether to enable ldiskfs.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I021df4471b618264f2ca62dc33bd59698ae1d7a6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
